N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 343.1 - Application

State Regulations

The fee schedule applicable to podiatry services shall be
the podiatry fee schedule in effect on the date on which the podiatry services
were rendered, regardless of the date of accident. Notes
